---
title: Caribbean-Inspired Turkey Bowls with Cashews and Pineapple Salsa
description: Inspired by Caribbean cuisine, these bowls bring a bit of sunshine to brighten up a grey day! Turkey tossed with mildly spiced poblanos and our Jerk Spice Blend has just the right amount of little heat. Sweet pineapple salsa balances out the flavours!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/bols-de-dinde-dinspiration-caribeenne-187a3296.jpg
